data.description: This charming home features a beautifully updated kitchen with three bedrooms with ample closet space and two aesthetically pleasing bathrooms. The quaintness of this home is unmatched with its charming touches everywhere you look. Tastefully personalized and designed, you'll feel at home as soon as you walk in. A lovely stainless steel farmhouse sink is featured in the kitchen along with stainless steel Samsung appliances. The backyard is partially turfed with a newly installed privacy fence and the covered back porch is perfect for outdoor entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Call today to schedule a showing! *Seller is willing to help pay some of buyer's closing cost depending on offer*
